                <p class="esasyj"><b><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Article 15. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">The right to security of purchase (work, service).</font></font></b></p> 
                <p class="esasyj"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">1.
         The consumer has the right to be safe while observing the terms of use,
