                <p class="esasyj"><b><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Article 16. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">The consumer\'s right to a good quality product (work, service) and to check its quality</font></font></b></p> 
