                <p class="esasyj"><b><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Article 17. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">The right of the consumer to receive a document confirming the purchase of goods (work, service) from the seller (executor)</font></font></b></p> 
