                <p class="esasyj"><b><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Article 18. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">The right of the consumer to receive a product (work, service) in a timely manner</font></font></b></p> 
                <p class="esasyj"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">The consumer has the right to receive the goods (work, service) within the terms specified in the contract.</font></font></p> 
                <p class="esasyj"><b><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Article 19. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Rights of the consumer in case of violation of the term of delivery of the product (work, service) by the contractor (executor)</font></font></b></p> 
                <p class="esasyj"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">1.
