                <p class="esasyj"><b><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Article 22. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Consumer rights in the event of a product (or service) defect</font></font></b></p> 
                <p class="esasyj"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">1.
